g-post_12.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post_12.html&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=1052593d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_12.html</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺開公司 (萬能界)<br />\n- 帶身份證去灣仔税局搞，俾$250，30分鐘搞掂 @businessfrontier<br />\n- 輕量級 &gt; 紡織界 $61/ 體育界 $2000/ 出版界 $1140 (撳個掣就得)<br />\n- 重量級 &gt; 商界 $3900/ 工業界 $2970/ 零售界 $1180/ 僱主聯合會 $4800<br />\n- 集中首選 &gt; 進出口界 $240+1320 (1年以上BR+商業地址）<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_57.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fblog-post_57.html&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=5e9d54e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_57.html</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺申請進出口牌 (進出口界）<br />\n只要有一年以上BR同埋商業地址，唔理你做咩生意，都可以向海關申請進出口牌，立即成為進出口界公司選民<br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"http://t.me/exportfrontier\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fexportfrontier&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=7b8d09bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/exportfrontier</a><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/exportfrontier/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fexportfrontier%2F&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=f0f7e46b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/exportfrontier/</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺掃黃店 (飲食界、零售界)<br />\n組隊幫手登記 &gt; <a href=\"https://forms.gle/am8LThtTL9r6joL17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fam8LThtTL9r6joL17&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=3aff196d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/am8LThtTL9r6joL17</a><br />\n掃黃店進度表 &gt; <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cEJGz6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cEJGz6&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=ee86ac6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cEJGz6</a><br />\n黃店名單 &gt; <a href=\"https://www.hkshoplist.com/select.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkshoplist.com%2Fselect.php&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=771222ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkshoplist.com/select.php</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺組社團 (文化界)<br />\n1. 齊集三人，須有相關文化資歷證明<br />\n2. 準備社團資料 - 宗旨/ 規章/ 擬辦活動<br />\n3. 準備個人資料 - 身分證副本/ 住址+會址證明 (3個月內)(銀行/水電煤單據)<br />\n4. 約組員出黎，互簽名，互交換文件<br />\n5. 寄出去 /親身交到警總 Done!<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_33.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post_33.html&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=55f096ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_33.html</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺每個香港人都可以拎三票<br />\n1. 地區個人票 (地方選區有得投）<br />\n2. 功能組別個人票 (正常人係超區)<br />\n3. 功能組別團體票(不可跟2同一界別)<br />\n<br />\n例子, 地方選區：香港島/ 功能界別(個人票)：超級區議會/ 功能界別(團體票)：飲食界<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_57.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post_57.html%3Fm%3D1&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=68a5fddc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_57.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n重點功能界別的whatapps Hotline<br />\nGeneral whatapps Hotline : 65391922<br />\n 體演文出whatapps Hotline : 66700860<br />\n 進出口界whatapps Hotline : 68461562<br />\n 飲食界whatapps Hotline : 9180 3949 / 66812202<br />\n 批發及零售whatapps Hotline : 65391922<br />\n<br />\n📣 請訂閱作戰研究院 Telegram Channel ➼ @FightResearch<br />\n戰術研究 | 抗爭資訊 | 時局分析 | 評論 | 趣事<br />\nCredits to 七起"},{"pid":"78c524902186bb3b385f91486ce4ae8683ec3fdf","tid":1927821,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202